474
00:26:53,113 --> 00:26:56,867
Okay. Okay. Then, well, thank you.
It's... I appreciate it.

475
00:26:56,950 --> 00:27:00,388
- -Absolutely. -Well, that's very, very kind of you.
- -Absolutely. -Well, that's very, very kind of you.

476
00:27:00,412 --> 00:27:02,706
