- No. This is what I wanna do.

494
00:27:41,703 --> 00:27:42,704
I'm trying to...

495
00:27:42,788 --> 00:27:45,791
- We're gonna do this.
- This... I mean… - Enough already. - $90. I insist.

496
00:27:45,874 --> 00:27:49,002
- Marty, no. No. It's fine.
- It's done.

497
00:27:49,086 --> 00:27:51,755
- It's do... It's not... [SIGHS]
- The money's in your hand.

498
00:27:57,177 --> 00:27:58,262
Thank you, Marty.

499
00:27:58,345 --> 00:28:00,114
- -You're something else. -There you go.
- -You're something else. -There you go.

500
00:28:00,138 --> 00:28:01,199
- Joe, I'm gonna…
- Thank you.

501
00:28:01,223 --> 00:28:02,700
- Oh, no, I got it.
- …give you your stool.

502
00:28:02,724 --> 00:28:04,869
