524
00:29:17,591 --> 00:29:19,277
- When you get cut…
- You didn't have to scream.

525
00:29:19,301 --> 00:29:21,136
- I wasn't screaming.
- You were screaming.

526
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:22,346
I was not screaming.

527
00:29:22,429 --> 00:29:24,765
[SIGHS] Fine. I... [SIGHS] Look, I-I...

528
